    {
      "id": "t2-006",
      "name": "Translate to French",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        -300,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "chat",
        "operation": "complete",
        "chatModel": "gpt-4.1-mini",
        "simplifyOutput": false,
        "prompt": {
          "messages": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a professional technical translator specializing in industrial fire protection and pump systems. You translate English WordPress post content to Canadian French (Qu\u00c3\u00a9b\u00c3\u00a9cois French) with 95%+ accuracy.\n\nCORE TRANSLATION RULES:\n1. Translate ONLY visible human-readable text. NEVER alter HTML tags, attributes, CSS classes, IDs, or href values.\n2. Preserve ALL HTML entities exactly as written: &amp; &nbsp; &mdash; &ndash; &lt; &gt; &quot; \u00e2\u20ac\u201d do not decode or re-encode them.\n3. Preserve ALL heading tags (h1\u00e2\u20ac\u201ch6), paragraph tags, list items, table cells \u00e2\u20ac\u201d translate only the text inside them.\n4. Do NOT translate content inside <code>, <pre>, <script>, or <style> tags.\n5. Translate alt text inside <img alt=\"...\"> tags, but leave src, width, height, class, id unchanged.\n6. Keep ALL hyperlinks (href values) in English \u00e2\u20ac\u201d only translate the visible anchor text if it is a plain English phrase.\n7. Keep brand names in English without exception: Tornatech, NFPA, UL, FM, IBC, ULC, CSA, ISO.\n8. Keep ALL model numbers, part numbers, standards references in English: \"NFPA 20-2022\", \"UL 448\", \"FM 1319\".\n9. Keep ALL numbers, units, measurements, and technical specifications unchanged.\n10. Maintain formal technical tone \u00e2\u20ac\u201d do not soften, simplify, or paraphrase. Match the register of the original.\n11. For ambiguous technical terms with no Qu\u00c3\u00a9b\u00c3\u00a9cois equivalent, keep English and add French in parentheses on first use only.\n12. Return ONLY a valid JSON object \u00e2\u20ac\u201d no markdown, no preamble:\n    {\"title\": \"<plain text translated title>\", \"content\": \"<full translated HTML>\"}\n\nTORNATECH GLOSSARY \u00e2\u20ac\u201d use these exact translations every time:\n- fire pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe \u00c3\u00a0 incendie\n- fire pump system \u00e2\u2020\u2019 syst\u00c3\u00a8me de pompe \u00c3\u00a0 incendie\n- pump controller \u00e2\u2020\u2019 contr\u00c3\u00b4leur de pompe\n- diesel fire pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe \u00c3\u00a0 incendie diesel\n- electric fire pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe \u00c3\u00a0 incendie \u00c3\u00a9lectrique\n- pressure relief valve \u00e2\u2020\u2019 soupape de d\u00c3\u00a9charge\n- jockey pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe pilote\n- pressure maintenance pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe de maintien de pression\n- suction header \u00e2\u2020\u2019 collecteur d'aspiration\n- discharge header \u00e2\u2020\u2019 collecteur de refoulement\n- flow rate \u00e2\u2020\u2019 d\u00c3\u00a9bit\n- working pressure \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pression de service\n- rated pressure \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pression nominale\n- shutoff pressure \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pression d'arr\u00c3\u00aat\n- horsepower (HP) \u00e2\u2020\u2019 puissance (ch)\n- impeller \u00e2\u2020\u2019 roue\n- priming \u00e2\u2020\u2019 amor\u00c3\u00a7age\n- alarm \u00e2\u2020\u2019 alarme\n- fire protection \u00e2\u2020\u2019 protection incendie\n- fire suppression \u00e2\u2020\u2019 suppression d'incendie\n- sprinkler system \u00e2\u2020\u2019 syst\u00c3\u00a8me de gicleurs\n- fire hydrant \u00e2\u2020\u2019 borne d'incendie\n- standpipe system \u00e2\u2020\u2019 syst\u00c3\u00a8me de colonne montante\n- wet standpipe \u00e2\u2020\u2019 colonne montante humide\n- dry standpipe \u00e2\u2020\u2019 colonne montante s\u00c3\u00a8che\n- test header \u00e2\u2020\u2019 collecteur d'essai\n- flow test \u00e2\u2020\u2019 essai de d\u00c3\u00a9bit\n- annual test \u00e2\u2020\u2019 essai annuel\n- commissioning \u00e2\u2020\u2019 mise en service\n- maintenance \u00e2\u2020\u2019 entretien\n- inspection \u00e2\u2020\u2019 inspection\n- listed / approved \u00e2\u2020\u2019 homologu\u00c3\u00a9 / approuv\u00c3\u00a9\n- authority having jurisdiction (AHJ) \u00e2\u2020\u2019 autorit\u00c3\u00a9 comp\u00c3\u00a9tente\n- end suction pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe \u00c3\u00a0 aspiration axiale\n- horizontal split case \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe \u00c3\u00a0 bo\u00c3\u00aetier fendu horizontal\n- vertical turbine \u00e2\u2020\u2019 pompe turbine verticale\n- booster pump \u00e2\u2020\u2019 surpresseur"
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "=Translate the following WordPress post from English to Canadian French (Qu\u00c3\u00a9b\u00c3\u00a9cois French).\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object with exactly two keys:\n- \"title\": the translated post title as plain text\n- \"content\": the full translated post body as HTML with all tags preserved\n\nDo not include any text outside the JSON object.\n\nTitle: {{ $json.title.rendered }}\n\nContent:\n{{ $json.content.rendered }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.2,
          "maxTokens": 16000
        }
      },
